# Pseudo-code ops

* FRCP rd, rs1 - pseudo-code alias for rd = 1.0 / rs1
* SINCOS - fused macro-op between FSIN and FCOS (issued in that order).
* SINCOSPI - fused macro-op between FSINPI and FCOSPI (issued in that order).

